title: What photos do you have on your phone? - Adminland - Quora

response.answer_text: Well, I've got a lot, but I'll just show you a sample of them. The first type of pictures I have is my pictures of the aquarium I volunteer at    Then I've got pictures of my dog… I've got a lot of these   Then I have selfies that you won't see because they are hideous… Oh and then my favorite, screenshots of conversations, but I can't show you them because it's against the rules and honestly some of them are kind of personal. Then I have memes, which I can show you    That last one kills me every time XD Then I have stuff I was going to make memes with but never got to actually doing it    Then I have random pictures that have no meaning    (Please don't ask why there is a pop tart on my knee, I honestly can't remember why) Then there are random screenshots that have no meaning    And then pictures I downloaded either for drawing or quora answers    And that's the end of it.
